546
00:23:48,208 --> 00:23:51,125
So are you
getting along with Roswaal?

547
00:23:51,208 --> 00:23:53,041
What were you two
talking about, anyway?

548
00:23:53,125 --> 00:23:56,000
- [coughs]
- Eh, I knew it.

549
00:23:56,083 --> 00:23:56,875
He was messing with you,
wasn't he?

550
00:23:56,958 --> 00:23:59,833
Perceptive, Mili.

551
00:23:59,916 --> 00:24:00,875
I feel like things
are gonna be even tougher

552
00:24:00,958 --> 00:24:01,875
than they were before.

553
00:24:01,958 --> 00:24:05,125
- Well, if you ask me,

554
00:24:05,208 --> 00:24:06,791
I think he's just afraid

555
00:24:06,875 --> 00:24:09,041
