everything that he's done.

556
00:24:09,125 --> 00:24:12,666
He only acts that way to try
and get everybody's attention.

557
00:24:12,750 --> 00:24:15,750
Honestly,
he can be such a child.

558
00:24:15,833 --> 00:24:18,125
- You really are amazing.
You know that?

559
00:24:18,208 --> 00:24:19,583
- You think so?

560
00:24:19,666 --> 00:24:21,250
[giggles] Well, thank you.

561
00:24:21,333 --> 00:24:23,666
And in case
you were wondering,

562
00:24:23,750 --> 00:24:26,083
I happen to feel
the same way about you, too.

563
00:24:29,333 --> 00:24:31,041
You know, Subaru,

564
00:24:31,125 --> 00:24:33,916
there's something I want to say
to my knight later,

565
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:36,541
maybe this evening
after all this is over.

566
00:24:36,625 --> 00:24:39,041
- What a coincidence,
'cause there's actually

567
00:24:39,125 --> 00:24:41,958
a lot that I was hoping
to say to you.

568
00:24:42,041 --> 00:24:42,666
Oh?

569
00:24:42,750 --> 00:24:45,833
- In that case, it's a promise.

570
00:24:46,875 --> 00:24:48,541
- [sighs]

571
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,041
- When everything's
finished here,

572
00:24:52,125 --> 00:24:54,666
the two of us can have a talk.

573
