to breaking promises,

576
00:24:58,458 --> 00:25:01,250
but when you invite me
to your room at night,

577
00:25:01,333 --> 00:25:02,625
just you and me,

578
00:25:02,708 --> 00:25:05,166
I assure you that's
not an option, not one bit!

579
00:25:05,250 --> 00:25:08,291
- Sorry, but I'm not really sure
what you mean by that.

580
00:25:10,416 --> 00:25:12,291
- All I'm saying
is that I can't wait

581
00:25:12,375 --> 00:25:15,208
to find out
what it is we'll talk about.

582
00:25:15,291 --> 00:25:17,916
- One evening
might not be enough for this.

583
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,750
- Hey, if it's
something that important,

584
00:25:19,833 --> 00:25:21,875
then I'll spend
as much time as it takes.

585
00:25:21,958 --> 00:25:26,291
After all, I am
your official knight! Okay?

586
00:25:26,375 --> 00:25:27,875
- O-Okay.

587
00:25:27,958 --> 00:25:30,083
- [chuckles]

588
00:25:30,166 --> 00:25:31,291
Eh?

589
00:25:33,666 --> 00:25:35,125
Seriously,
don't worry about it.

590
00:25:35,208 --> 00:25:37,583
Regardless
of what you tell me,

591
00:25:37,666 --> 00:25:39,750
my feelings for you
won't change.

592
00:25:39,833 --> 00:25:41,625
- [gasps] Subaru.

593
00:25:41,708 --> 00:25:43,708
- What happens
in the beginning or the middle

594
00:25:43,791 --> 00:25:45,083
isn't what really matters.

595
00:25:45,166 --> 00:25:46,916
It's the end that counts.

596
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:49,250
And despite how things
actually started,

597
00:25:49,333 --> 00:25:52,208
